task.summary: Default task
Added JSON framework to all database objects
Added source probing

Added url separated from filename for sources. Added auto reconnect after error from select query due to database connection timeout. Added process manager for encode and probe services. Updated bootstrap to v4.1.1. Added process table to track various lone running processes.
Added more controls for process management. Added encoded progress table and support objects to keep track of encoding progress over time.
Updated libraries. Updated project pom to allow maven display updated check. Updated flyway to use new schema history table.
Added Full support for saving and loading JSON Objects from the database. Generalised probe function. Probe is run on all new sources automatically.

Updated Angular JS. Added auto probing of new sources. Added extra probe info about the source when selecting it on the databaseadmin screen. Added process screen listing all unencoded sources. Extended JSON framework to allow embedded objects to also return their json values.
Added progress bars for encoding for both passes. Added calculated JS functions for duration and resolution. Added live update button to current processes.
Added Splitter to cut files at specific times. Added data files for Clips.
Can now remove marks. Can now jump to specific mark in video display.
Can now remove marks. Can now jump to specific mark in video display.
Added saving/loading/displaying marks in the database to be in sync with what is shown on the page.
Added making, removing clips. Made clips use mark objects. Few other bug fixes.
Added single DBObject to be added to JSONContainer. New UUID is returned from request to create new clip and mark.
Move buttons around on dba page.
Make it so that Request classes are auto built.
Able to select a start and end mark for a clip, updates server and client fully.
Able to lock in selection of start and end marks for a clip. Added server request service via angular to handle all http requests.
Finished implementation of 2 pass encoder to give webm video when times are chosen. Made it so processes are auto cleaned when finished.
Fixed prober processes from conflicting with each other.
Updated font-awesome to 5.0.13
Updated font-awesome to 5.0.13
Clips are now probed once split to see the total frames. Clips now have encoded progress. Processes page now shows clips encoding progress.
Processes are now started with process builder and input and error streams are combined. Corrected bug with duration of clips after probing.
Upgraded buttons to be bootstrap buttons.
Fixed duplicate list of Marks in database admin page.
Added data table screen to show people. Added way to import people. Added base classes to support people/appearances.
Added people form to add a new person and also a table to display all people.
